<headline>Special Weather Statement issued January 02 at 8:14PM MST  by NWS GreatFalls</headline>
<description>...Patchy Dense Fog...
Locations across the Helena Valley can see patchy dense fog
between 11 PM tonight and 10 AM tomorrow morning. Visibility could
be reduced to less than one mile. When traveling during the
morning, use extra caution while driving by slowing down when you
encounter fog and leaving plenty of distance ahead of you.</description>
